<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3612938>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. General characteristics of Apenesia. A. Palpi; B. Mesosoma, dorsal view, C. Forewing; D. Hind wing; E–G. Genitalia: E. Basivolsella, internal view; F. Genitalia, dorsal view; G. Detail at higher magnifications of apical projection on basiparamere apex, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3612938/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3612990>
    dc:description "FIGURE 26. Body. A. Apenesia dominica; B. Apenesia flavipes; C. Apenesia formosa; D. Apenesia levis, E. Apenesia nigra; F. Apenesia proxima; G. Apenesia substriata; H. Apenesia unicolor; I. Apenesia vaurieorum. (Scale 250µm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3612990/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3612986>
    dc:description "FIGURE 24. Head. A. Apenesia azeda; B. Apenesia celiela; C. Apenesia conradti; D. Apenesia sahyadrica. Mandible. E. Apenesia azeda; F. Apenesia celiela; G. Apenesia conradti; H. Apenesia sahyadrica. Lateral mesosoma. I. Apenesia conradti; J. Apenesia parasitica." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3612986/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3612988>
    dc:description "FIGURE 25. Dorsal mesosoma. A. Apenesia azeda; B. Apenesia celiela; C. Apenesia conradti; D. Apenesia parasitica, E. Apenesia sahyadrica. Body. F. Apenesia amazonica; G. Apenesia amoena; H. Apenesia bicolor; I. Apenesia chontaica; J. Apenesia delicata. (Scale bar F–J 250µm)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3612988/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

